---
import Bibliography from "../Bibliography.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="space-y-24 mt-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <section class="relative animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-700">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div
                class="p-4 bg-teal-100 dark:bg-teal-900/30 rounded-2xl text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-teal-500/10"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:information-variant" class="w-8 h-8" />
            </div>
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter"
            >
                ¿Qué es la Terapia de Muesca?
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div
            class="prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed tracking-wide"
        >
            <p>
                La <strong>Terapia de Muesca</strong> (<em>Notch Therapy</em>) es una técnica
                innovadora de tratamiento auditivo diseñada específicamente para el <strong
                    >tinnitus tonal</strong
                >—ese pitido constante en una frecuencia específica que no cesa.
            </p>
            <p>
                En lugar de simplemente "tapar" el ruido, esta técnica utiliza un sonido de banda
                ancha (como ruido blanco) al que se le ha eliminado la frecuencia exacta de tu
                zumbido. Al privar al cerebro de estímulos en esa frecuencia específica, se busca
                reducir la hiperactividad neuronal en la corteza auditiva mediante <strong
                    >inhibición lateral</strong
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-700 delay-150">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-12">
            <div
                class="p-4 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-2xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-indigo-500/10"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:palette-swatch" class="w-8 h-8" />
            </div>
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter"
            >
                Tipos de Ruido
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700/60 hover:border-teal-400 dark:hover:border-teal-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-teal-500/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-[2rem]"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-teal-50 dark:group-hover:bg-teal-900/30 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:waves"
                            class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-teal-500 transition-colors"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                        Ruido Blanco
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Todas las frecuencias a la misma intensidad. Ideal para <strong
                            >enmascaramiento total</strong
                        > y bloqueo de sonidos externos.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700/60 hover:border-pink-400 dark:hover:border-pink-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-pink-500/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-[2rem]"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-pink-50 dark:group-hover:bg-pink-900/30 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:water"
                            class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                        Ruido Rosa
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Más suave y equilibrado. Similar a la lluvia o el viento. Reduce la fatiga
                        auditiva en sesiones largas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700/60 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-amber-500/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-[2rem]"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-amber-50 dark:group-hover:bg-amber-900/30 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:image-filter-hdr"
                            class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                        Ruido Marrón
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Profundo y retumbante. Frecuencias graves dominantes. Evoca truenos lejanos.
                        Perfecto para <strong>dormir</strong>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-700 delay-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-12">
            <div
                class="p-4 bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 rounded-2xl text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-emerald-500/10"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:clipboard-check" class="w-8 h-8" />
            </div>
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter"
            >
                Instrucciones
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700/60"
        >
            <ol class="space-y-10">
                <li class="flex gap-6 items-start">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-black text-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600"
                        >1</span
                    >
                    <div class="pt-1">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                            Preparación
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                            Encuentra un entorno silencioso y usa auriculares de buena calidad
                            (preferiblemente de respuesta plana).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-6 items-start">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-black text-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600"
                        >2</span
                    >
                    <div class="pt-1">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                            Localización
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                            Mueve el <strong>deslizador de frecuencia</strong>. Cuando el sonido de
                            la app coincida con tu tinnitus, sentirás que se "cancelan" o mezclan.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-6 items-start">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-black text-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600"
                        >3</span
                    >
                    <div class="pt-1">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                            Tratamiento
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                            Ajusta el volumen al "punto de mezcla" (audible pero sin tapar tu
                            tinnitus). Escucha durante 15-30 minutos.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>

            <div
                class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-rose-50 dark:bg-rose-900/10 border border-rose-100 dark:border-rose-500/20"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:alert-decagram" class="w-8 h-8 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0" />
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <p
                        class="text-rose-700 dark:text-rose-200 text-base leading-relaxed font-medium"
                    >
                        Esta herramienta es para bienestar general. Si experimentas dolor, mareos o
                        empeoramiento, suspende el uso y consulta a un especialista.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <Bibliography
        links={[
            {
                name: "Tinnitus Notch Therapy - American Academy of Audiology",
                url: "https://www.audiology.org/",
            },
            {
                name: "Colors of Noise explained - Wikipedia",
